<subSubSection id="A8D0653DFFD1FFB75889FCEAFBDE6520" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="E07536B6FFD1FFB75889FCEAFBDE6520" blockId="28.[151,1437,834,1113]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
This family contains over 3,000 species (
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75A7CFCEAFCD862F8" author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T." box="[610,875,871,897]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" refId="ref350035" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T. (2020) Systema Dipterorum. Version 2. 7. Available from: http: // www. diptera. org / (accessed 30 August 2020)" type="url" year="2020">Evenhuis &amp; Pape 2020</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75B63FCEAFB8862F8" author="Rondani, C." box="[893,1083,870,897]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="166 - 191" refId="ref370972" refString="Rondani, C. (1875 b) Species italicae ordinis dipterorum (Muscaria Rndn.) collectae et observatae. Stirps XXIII Agromyzinae. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 7 (3), 166 - 191." type="journal article" year="1875">Rondani (1875b)</bibRefCitation>
described 15 Palaearctic nominal species, six considered as valid, six as junior synonyms and three as 
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FFD1FFB75BC2FC06FBC962DC" box="[988,1146,907,933]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
nomina 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FFD1FFB75C24FC06FBC962DC" baseAuthorityName="Zetterstedt" baseAuthorityYear="1838" box="[1082,1146,907,933]" class="Insecta" family="Stratiomyidae" genus="Exodontha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dubia">dubia</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75C94FC06FAA562DC" author="Papp, L." box="[1162,1302,907,933]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" refId="ref363209" refString="Papp, L. (1984 b) Family Agromyzidae. In: Soos, A. &amp; Papp, L. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera. Volume 9. Micropezidae - Agromyzidae. Elsevier Science Publishers, Amsterdam &amp; Akademiai Kiado, Budapest, pp. 263 - 343." type="book" year="1984">Papp 1984b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75D3DFC06FE8D62B0" author="Spencer, K. A. &amp; Martinez, M." pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="253 - 271" refId="ref374690" refString="Spencer, K. A. &amp; Martinez, M. (1987) Additions and corrections to the Agromyzidae section of the catalogue of Palearctic Diptera (Papp, 1984). Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, New Series, 23 (3), 253 - 271." type="journal article" year="1987">Spencer &amp; Martinez 1987</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75956FC22FD8862B0" author="Canzoneri, S. &amp; Gorodkov, K. &amp; Krivosheina, P. &amp; Munari, L. &amp; Nartshuk, E. &amp; Papp, L. &amp; Suss, L." box="[328,571,942,969]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="1 - 27" refId="ref346907" refString="Canzoneri, S., Gorodkov, K., Krivosheina, P., Munari, L., Nartshuk, E., Papp, L. &amp; Suss, L. (1995) Diptera Opomyzoidea, Carnoidea, Sphaeroceroidea. In: Minelli, A., Ruffo, S. &amp; La Posta, S. (Eds.), Checklist delle specie della fauna italiana. 75. Calderini, Bologna, pp. 1 - 27." type="book chapter" year="1995">
Canzoneri 
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FFD1FFB759DCFC22FE4962B0" box="[450,506,943,969]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">et al.</emphasis>
1995
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75A58FC22FCF862B0" author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T." box="[582,843,943,969]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" refId="ref350035" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T. (2020) Systema Dipterorum. Version 2. 7. Available from: http: // www. diptera. org / (accessed 30 August 2020)" type="url" year="2020">Evenhuis &amp; Pape 2020</bibRefCitation>
). In his paper on the Rondani types at 
<collectionCode id="86DBAE73FFD1FFB75CEAFC22FAFB62B0" box="[1268,1352,943,969]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/xa0v-1feb" name="Museo di Zoologia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">MZUB</collectionCode>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75D4CFC22FF436294" author="Morge, G." pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="81 - 92" refId="ref360282" refString="Morge, G. (1959 b) Die &quot; amtliche &quot; Dipteren-Sammlung von Prof. Camillo Rondani. Naturkundliches Jahrbuch der Stadt Linz, 6, 81 - 92." type="journal article" year="1959">Morge (1959b)</bibRefCitation>
listed three names (
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FFD1FFB759CDFC5EFDD56294" box="[467,614,979,1005]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
nomina 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FFD1FFB75A30FC5EFDD56294" authorityName="Maibach et al." authorityYear="1994" baseAuthorityName="Macquart" baseAuthorityYear="1829" box="[558,614,979,1005]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Paxillaceae" genus="Melanogaster" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="nuda">nuda</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
) that he attributed to Rondani. Kenneth A. Spencer examined the 
<collectionCode id="86DBAE73FFD1FFB75D50FC5EFA2F6294" box="[1358,1436,979,1005]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/mvk4-k796" name="Museo Zoologico La Specola, Universita di Firenze" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">MZUF</collectionCode>
types without publishing any 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FFD1FFB759FDFC7AFDF96568" box="[483,586,1015,1041]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">lectotype</typeStatus>
designation (
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FFD1FFB75AFFFC7AFBBA6568" author="Spencer, K. A. &amp; Martinez, M." box="[737,1033,1015,1041]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="253 - 271" refId="ref374690" refString="Spencer, K. A. &amp; Martinez, M. (1987) Additions and corrections to the Agromyzidae section of the catalogue of Palearctic Diptera (Papp, 1984). Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, New Series, 23 (3), 253 - 271." type="journal article" year="1987">Spencer &amp; Martinez 1987</bibRefCitation>
). Here, we designate a 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FFD1FFB75D10FC7AFAC66568" box="[1294,1397,1015,1041]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">lectotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FFD1FFB75889FB96FDE7654C" authority="Rondani, 1875" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1875" box="[151,596,1050,1077]" genus="Domomyza" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" rank="species" species="anthracipes">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FFD1FFB75889FB96FE10654C" box="[151,419,1051,1077]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Domomyza anthracipes</emphasis>
Rondani, 1875
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FFD1FFB75A8EFB96FB9F654C" authority="Rondani, 1875" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1875" box="[656,1068,1050,1077]" genus="Domomyza" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" rank="species" species="frontella">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FFD1FFB75A8EFB96FCC4654C" box="[656,887,1051,1077]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Domomyza frontella</emphasis>
Rondani, 1875
</taxonomicName>
. Except for 
<specimenCount id="F6CCFD3FFFD1FFB75CA5FB96FAE2654C" box="[1211,1361,1051,1077]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" type="generic" typeStatus="syntypes">two syntypes</specimenCount>
in the 
<collectionCode id="86DBAE73FFD1FFB75889FBB2FF556520" box="[151,230,1087,1113]" country="Sweden" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34994" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34994" name="Lund University" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">MZLU</collectionCode>
and one in the 
<collectionCode id="86DBAE73FFD1FFB7598CFBB2FE556520" box="[402,486,1087,1113]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/xa0v-1feb" name="Museo di Zoologia" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">MZUB</collectionCode>
, the type material for all nominal species is in the 
<collectionCode id="86DBAE73FFD1FFB75C07FBB2FBDB6520" box="[1049,1128,1087,1113]" country="Italy" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/mvk4-k796" name="Museo Zoologico La Specola, Universita di Firenze" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">MZUF</collectionCode>
.
</paragraph>
